      "message": "Sorry. This was not obvious. Here is the argument for the translation of this if-statement to the if-statement in translateVerticesIfNeeded().\n\nMoving the condition into calculate_translation we get...\nif (!this-\u003edrawAsDistanceFields() \u0026\u0026 !this-\u003eneedsTransform()) {\n   // vertices are in device space\n} else {\n   // vertices are in source space\n}\n\nbecomes...\n\nif (!(this-\u003edrawAsDistanceFields() || this-\u003eneedsTransform())) {\n   // vertices are in device space\n} else {\n   // vertices are in source space\n}\n\nbecomes...\n\nif (this-\u003edrawAsDistanceFields() || this-\u003eneedsTransform()) {\n   // vertices are in source space\n} else {\n   // vertices are in device space\n}\n\nNow, drawAsDistanceFields is {return fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedSDF;} and needsTransform() is\nreturn fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedPath\n           || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedMask\n           || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedSDFT;\n\nthe if statement becomes\n\nif (fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedSDF || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedPath\n           || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedMask\n           || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedSDFT) ...\n\nbecomes\nif (fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedPath\n           || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedMask\n           || fType \u003d\u003d kTransformedSDFT) ...\n\nbecomes\nif (this-\u003eneedsTransform())...",
